{"id":"678e0848-6b7d-4259-b503-9ac121f3112c","name":"Blaze the Cat","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Being the princess of the Sol Empire, and guardian of the Sol Emeralds, Blaze is a stoic and regal protector who prioritizes the safety of her home and people. Somewhat hesitant to make friends, her experiences with Sonic the Hedgehog and his friends convinced her to open up to others, and learn the value of relationships with others.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 104, 204);\"><strong>Appears in the </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 225, 90);\"><strong><em>Sonic the Hedgehog</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 104, 204);\"><strong><em> </em>franchise.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x58P-Wljw4jQyhBIpGLOJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 150, 150);\">(Please leave reviews if I can improve the character or if you enjoy the character. Your ratings give me endorphins.)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Update 10/10: Lorebook added consisting of most mainline game canon. May add IDW at a later date.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3yvsT5C3BbhwM9Nppeyh4.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>RECOMMENDED BOT LINKS:</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/00ab9e55-d7ad-4b7d-8d26-35e04dd6413a_character-amy-rose\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong>Amy Rose</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 136, 255);\"><strong><em>